. Research conclusion: Telegram private DM is poor for this; a private Telegram group with Topics is the best route if he wants visible separation inside Telegram.\n- For Telegram topics/groups with OpenClaw, the key config findings were:\n  - parent group allowlistin\n\nSource: memory/2026-03-29.md#L18-L26","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-03-29.md#L18-L26"}],"provider":"openai","model":"text-embedding-3-small","citations":"auto","mode":"hybrid"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774880988983}}
