iretório de review e o histórico local para reconstruir com precisão o que aqueles agentes produziram, em vez de adivinhar.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0047bd771936d8e20169ca893b5ba88195992241eb10792729\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"commentary\\\"}\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_Zf7pXdSaXpP6zdcWAxGixl23|fc_0047bd771936d8e20169ca893e9cd481959b6d6d9c6e792e2c\",\n              \"name\": \"exec\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"command\": \"Get-ChildItem -Force -LiteralPath 'C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\reviews\\\\tobias_review_29mar' | Select-Object Name,FullName,Mode,Length,LastWriteTime | Format-Table -AutoSize\",\n                \"yieldMs\": 10000,\n                \"workdir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"\n              },\n              \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"command\\\":\\\"Get-ChildItem -Force -LiteralPath 'C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\User-OEM\\\\\\\\Desktop\\\\\\\\content-factory\\\\\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\\\\\reviews\\\\\\\\tobias_review_29mar' | Select-Object Name,FullName,Mode,Length,LastWriteTime | Format-Table -AutoSize\\\",\\\"yieldMs\\\":10000,\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\User-OEM\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\workspace\\\"}\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_rBDDPAsVVUHdSWtblQgfT3PT|fc_0047bd771936d8e20169ca893e9ce48195a6eea68801bdeece\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"limit\": 50,\n                \"activeMinutes\": 10080,\n                \"messageLimit\": 2\n              },\n              \"partialJson\": \"{\\\"limit\\\":50,\\\"activeMinutes\\\":10080,\\\"messageLimit\\\":2}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 788,\n            \"output\": 178,\n            \"totalTokens\": 18502,\n            \"cacheRead\": 17536,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.009024\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774881080864,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0047bd771936d8e20169ca893a87b88195b108d6b98ea69f7f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"255a60cf\",\n            \"seq\": 17\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:0d8719eb-b287-49cd-ae2e-5b7f7a2e2551\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"label\": \"watchdog-mvp-reconciler\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-0d8719eb-b287-49cd-ae2e-5b7f7a2e2551\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774877364780,\n      \"sessionId\": \"5011acc2-400b-4819-98ee-0dfa2ebbc124\",\n      \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 1000000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 85092,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 1.1475174000000001,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774876965842,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774877319530,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 344365,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\5011acc2-400b-4819-98ee-0dfa2ebbc124.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Everything is clean. Here's the complete summary:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Entregáveis\\n\\n### 1. Diagnóstico\\n\\n**Problema raiz:** `watchdog.py` confia 100% em `active_tasks.json` sem consultar o runtime. O campo `status` só muda se o agente que lançou a task o actualizar explicitamente — o que não acontece quando a session termina silenciosamente ou é esquecida.\\n\\n**Caso concreto:** Task `retest_claude_code_sidecar_20260328_160800` estava como `running` há +2 dias. Em `subagents/runs.json` o run correspondente (`childSessionKey: agent:main:subagent:f45bf7bf...`) tinha `endedAt`, `endedReason: subagent-complete`, `outcome.status: ok`. A task estava morta mas gerava pings a cada 10 minutos.\\n\\n### 2. Estados mínimos implementados\\n\\n`spawned → running → stalled → orphaned` (escalada por tempo, sem runtime)  \\n`running → completed / failed` (reconciliado contra `runs.json`)\\n\\n### 3. Implementação\\n\\n**Ficheiros criados:**\\n- `task_watchdog/reconciler.py` — lógica de reconciliação (225 linhas). Lê `subagents/runs.json`, pesquisa por `childSessionKey`, classifica o run, e actualiza o status da task sem inventar infra externa.\\n\\n**Ficheiros alterados:**\\n- `task_watchdog/watchdog.py` — `main()` chama `reconcile_all()` antes do `evaluate_tasks()`, com fallback silencioso se o reconciler falhar. `evaluate_tasks()` passou a suportar `spawned`, `stalled`, e `orphaned`. Deduplicação por `terminalNotifiedStatus` impede notificações repetidas.\\n\\n**Ficheiro de documentação criado:**\\n- `task_watchdog/RECONCILER_NOTES.md` — diagnóstico, arquitectura, thresholds, notas de teste.\\n\\n### 4. Validado em execução\\n\\n- Primeira run: reconciliou zombie → `completed`, notificou uma vez, arquivou em `task_history.jsonl`, removeu de `active_tasks.json`\\n- Segunda run: zero notificações falsas, `remaining: []`, `notifications: []`\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n          \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 1,\n            \"output\": 580,\n            \"totalTokens\": 85672,\n            \"cacheRead\": 84914,\