\\\\reviews\\\\tobias_review_29mar\\\\22_session_battle_board.md`\\n\\nO board está comprimido e operacional, cobrindo:\\n- ordem recomendada para a sessão ao vivo\\n- status por setor: ready / blocked / do later\\n- decisões principais a fechar live\\n- batches prontos para entregar ao Claude Code\\n- traps a evitar\\n- cadence sugerida da reunião/workflow\\n- checklist de fecho\\n\\nPonto central do board:\\n- a sessão deve optimizar para **freeze de contratos + shared infra + lote P0 implementável**\\n- e **evitar cair em VO pleno / S9 / S6 browser-heavy cedo demais**.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0720d1a20670abea0169c937380eac819181ebf262c7eff349\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 22844,\n            \"output\": 167,\n            \"totalTokens\": 23011,\n            \"cacheRead\": 0,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.05961500000000001\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774794545611,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0720d1a20670abea0169c937335d588191b6290aca27e01140\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"9c1a98e3\",\n            \"seq\": 10\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:e3aae318-4f32-4b3e-a743-69796c328349\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"spawnedBy\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"label\": \"audit-block-b\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-e3aae318-4f32-4b3e-a743-69796c328349\",\n      \"parentSessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774794184945,\n      \"sessionId\": \"c084f1dd-51dc-