\n- Main emphasis is on **contract freeze before heavy coding**, especially:\n  - S7 schema freeze\n  - S8 lettering split + soundtrack ownership\n  - S9 reviewer set / naming / resolution\n  - S10 idempotency + finalization manifest / checkpoint convention\n\nIf needed, the next natural step would be turning this into a **live session checklist version** or a **Claude Code task breakdown by file/module**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03505f84b5d41c100169c93784a60c8191b368f3984aa73f22\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":134,"output":268,"totalTokens":30610,"cacheRead":30208,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.011907000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774794621538,"responseId":"resp_03505f84b5d41c100169c9377f3be08191bafe959afe79afdd","__openclaw":{"id":"1c5b83f2","seq":11}}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:edcb65a3-61e3-4a11-b36c-2db4f4d0292f","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:main:main","label":"session-pack-A","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-edcb65a3-61e3-4a11-b36c-2db4f4d0292f","parentSessionKey":"agent:main:main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774794630077,"sessionId":"31da92a9-1199-4822-935d-c35a51dd381e","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":29796,"estimatedCostUsd":0.171842,"status":"done","startedAt":1774794484101,"endedAt":1774794621069,"runtimeMs":132049,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\31da92a9-1199-4822-935d-c35a51dd381e.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Concluído.\n\nCriei o ficheiro:\n- `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\reviews\\tobias_review_29mar\\23_sector_execution_plan_A.md`\n\nO pack está estruturado para PM, VO, S1, S2 e S3 com os 9 blocos pedidos para cada um:\n- missão\n- sólido\n- ambíguo/perigoso\n- sequência concreta\n- checklist por operador\n- decisões live do Lucca\n- o que Claude Code pode fazer já\n- reuse V3 vs net-new\n- 3 primeiras tasks concretas\n\nPontos relevantes para o requester:\n- Mantive o foco em execução prática, não teoria.\n- Usei apenas o material das reviews/docs indicadas.\n- Forcei a lógica de **contract freeze primeiro**, porque isso aparece como risco estrutural recorrente em quase todos os componentes.\n- Em S2 deixei explícito que a primeira decisão é matar a bifurcação doc vs mirror antes de implementação séria.\n- No VO deixei claro que o caminho correcto é **VO mínimo depois dos contratos core**, não VO pleno cedo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ecb2fb499bb29d00169c93779bcb88191924618207287355d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":228,"output":242,"totalTokens":30038,"cacheRead":29568,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.011591999999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774794614972,"responseId":"resp_0ecb2fb499bb29d00169c93778b9c08191ad0aea7da9ad8147","__openclaw":{"id":"5c62b302","seq":12}}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:bce133f4-39ae-4582-9c63-4ec2d5c0522e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:main:main","label":"claude-code-backlog","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-bce133f4-39ae-4582-9c63-4ec2d5c0522e","parentSessionKey":"agent:main:main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774794617356,"sessionId":"9fe9792b-f890-45be-98d5-5f47b76e6e70","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":50286,"estimatedCostUsd":0.2521385,"status":"done","startedAt":1774794446810,"endedAt":1774794608647,"runtimeMs":160541,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\9fe9792b-f890-45be-98d5-5f47b76e6e70.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done — I created:\n\n- `reviews\\tobias_review_29mar\\26_claude_code_task_backlog.md`\n\nWhat it contains:\n- backlog grouped by implementation phase\n- each task includes:\n  - title\n  - why it matters\n  - dependencies\n  - likely files/modules to touch\n  - done criteria\n  - priority (P0/P1)\n- strong bias toward practical engineering bundles, not micro-tasks\n- implementation order aligned with the audit:\n  - contract freeze\n  - shared substrate\n  - PM + wrappers\n  - S1/S2/S4\n  - S3/S5/S6\n  - S7/S8\n  - S9/S10\n  - VO last\n\nRelevant note:\n- the repo appears to be mostly documentation + workspace mirror right now, with no established runtime code tree yet, so I framed likely implementation targets as new shared runtime modules (`runtime/` or `src/`) plus the existing docs/mirror areas that Claude Code will need to align while implementing.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043858592f200ba20169c9376dfb44819184c4eb84b781e060\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":238,"output":218,"totalTokens":50504,"cacheRead":50048,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.016377}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774794603621,"responseId":"resp_043858592f200ba20169c9376d58748191aacbb455fb5e0fba","__openclaw":{"id":"c6408d50","seq":14}}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:dc24faab-3aae-482a-a304-961eabe592a2","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","spawnedBy":"agent:main:main","label":"session-battle-board","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-dc24faab-3aae-482a-a304-961eabe592a2","parentSessionKey":"agent:main:main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774794562922,"sessionId":"dc92ec7d-5e11-408b-b1b2-bb2094b4e858","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":22844,"estimatedCostUsd":0.1424165,"status":"done","startedAt":1774794485741,"endedAt":1774794553596,"runtimeMs":62886,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\dc92ec7d-5e11-408b-b1b2-b