 actualiza��o da tracking sheet\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\12_VIDEO_DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md:268:| 28 Mar 2026 | s10_finalization/ adicionado: compressed.mp4, upload_receipt, sheets_update, production_report |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:10:S10 e o ultimo setor do pipeline. Recebe video_final.mp4 do S9, comprime, strip metadata, faz upload para Google Drive, actualiza tracking sheets, libera script lock, e compila production report com metricas de todo o pipeline (S1-S10). Depois dele, o video esta pronto para publicacao manual no YouTube.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:39:- Upload resumavel (chunks 10MB) para pasta `config[\"drive_folder_{lang}\"]` no Google Drive\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:44:#### sheets_tracker\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:63:- Client existente: `google_sheets.py` do V3\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:85:- **Skills** (4x Python): Deterministicas, sem LLM -- FFmpeg, Google Drive API, Google Sheets API, leitura de checkpoints\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:104:FASE 2: Upload Google Drive\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:110:FASE 3: Update Sheets + Release Lock\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:111:sheets_tracker:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\branches\\10_FINALIZATION.md:195:### sheets_tracker output\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto