.md:10:+-- sheets_tracker         [Skill Python] Actualiza sheet + release lock\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\AGENTS.md:34:7. Invoca `sheets_tracker` -- append 15 campos + release script lock\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\CONTEXT.md:26:| Google Drive | `video_final_compressed.mp4` | Video comprimido e sem metadata |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\CONTEXT.md:27:| Google Sheets | Row na tracking sheet | 15 campos + script lock released |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\CONTEXT.md:37:- **Google Drive API** -- upload resumavel\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\CONTEXT.md:38:- **Google Sheets API** -- append row + update cell\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\CONTEXT.md:51:- Video disponivel no Google Drive para download\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\IDENTITY.md:7:A minha funcao e coordenar 4 skills Python sequenciais para receber o video_final.mp4 do S9, comprimir, strip metadata, fazer upload para Google Drive, actualizar tracking sheets, liberar script lock, e compilar production report com metricas de todo o pipeline (S1-S10).\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\IDENTITY.md:31:4. **Upload para Google Drive** via drive_uploader (skill Python, chunks resumaveis 10MB)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\IDENTITY.md:32:5. **Actualizo tracking sheet** via sheets_tracker (skill Python, 15 campos + release lock)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\MEMORY.md:33:| Sheets `403 Forbidden` | Permissao de escrita removida | Re-autorizar service account |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\MEMORY.md:34:| Sheets `400 Bad Request` | Campos com formato invalido | Truncar script a 5000 chars, escapar caracteres especiais |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\MEMORY.md:42:| Quota diaria | 750GB/dia upload limit Google Drive | Esperar reset (meia-noite PT) ou usar outra conta |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\RULES.md:9:3. **sheets_tracker** -- precisa do URL do Drive\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\RULES.md:29:### R4 -- Upload Drive ANTES de Update Sheets\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\RULES.md:30:O upload para Google Drive DEVE completar com sucesso ANTES de actualizar a tracking sheet. A sheet precisa do URL do Drive para o campo \"youtube url\" (link de download).\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\RULES.md:32:Sequencia: compress -> upload -> sheets. NUNCA inverter.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\RULES.md:41:| sheets_tracker | Permissao negada, sheet nao encontrada | Retry com backoff (1s, 3s, 9s) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\TOOLS.md:10:| `drive_uploader` | Python | Upload resumavel para Google Drive |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\TOOLS.md:11:| `sheets_tracker` | Python | Actualiza tracking sheet + release script lock |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\TOOLS.md:85:#### sheets_tracker\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\TOOLS.md:127:**Client**: `google_sheets.py` do Content Factory V3 (`shared/clients/google_sheets.py`)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\branches\\10_finalization\\TOOLS.md:164:[sheets_tracker]\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\AGENTS.md:1:# AGENTS.md - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\CONTEXT.md:1:# Context - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\CONTEXT.md:5:- **Fase**: 1 - PM accionado manualmente pelo Tobias (sem cron)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\CONTEXT.md:8:- **PUB sheet**: Google Sheets, tab PUB, acesso via service account\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\CONTEXT.md:9:- **Skill read_pub**: N�O IMPLEMENTADA AINDA - at� estar pronta, dados da PUB s�o fornecidos manualmente pelo Tobias/Lucca\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\CONTEXT.md:20:O PM n�o interage com o pipeline directamente. Gera um job JSON  Video Orchestrator executa.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\IDENTITY.md:1:# Identity - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\IDENTITY.md:18:2. L�s a planilha PUB no Google Sheets (fonte da verdade)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\IDENTITY.md:54:TU (PM) - decides O QUE produzir\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\MEMORY.md:1:# Memory - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\RULES.md:1:# Rules - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\SCHEDULE.md:1:# Schedule - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\SCHEDULE.md:4:Quando o PM precisa da lista de canais activos, l� este ficheiro.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\TOOLS.md:1:# Tools - Production Manager\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\TOOLS.md:3:## 1. Skill: read_pub (PUB Sheet)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\TOOLS.md:8:Uma skill nativa do OpenClaw que l� a planilha PUB via Google Sheets API, calcula runways de todos os canais, e devolve um JSON ordenado por urg�ncia.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\TOOLS.md:12:skills/read_pub/\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\workspace_mirror\\production_manager\\TOOLS.md:14:��� read_pub.py     <- script Python\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_co