{"type":"message","id":"9c873dbb","parentId":"679daeac","timestamp":"2026-03-30T18:56:08.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Vou fazer essa última ronda focada no V3 para fechar ratio/validation, alignment e o shape mais reaproveitável do output de áudio antes de te trazer o desenho final do S2.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0047bd771936d8e20169cac7402c4081959a5a015873dc9ccf\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_jfQRfH2uiF5f91ejFu6NWebK|fc_0047bd771936d8e20169cac747a0048195b0dcbbd1adb2f2e8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$root='C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared'; Get-ChildItem -LiteralPath $root -Recurse -File -Include *.py,*.md,*.json,*.yaml,*.yml,*.txt | Select-String -Pattern 'transcription_validator','ratio match','match threshold','word match','timestamp_aligner','align_words','word_timestamps','audio_clip','duration_actual','scene_bible' | ForEach-Object { \"{0}:{1}:{2}\" -f $_.Path,$_.LineNumber,$_.Line.Trim() } | Select-Object -First 400","yieldMs":10000,"workdir":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"$root='C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\content_factory_v3\\\\shared'; Get-ChildItem -LiteralPath $root -Recurse -File -Include *.py,*.md,*.json,*.yaml,*.yml,*.txt | Select-String -Pattern 'transcription_validator','ratio match','match threshold','word match','timestamp_aligner','align_words','word_timestamps','audio_clip','duration_actual','scene_bible' | ForEach-Object { \\\"{0}:{1}:{2}\\\" -f $_.Path,$_.LineNumber,$_.Line.Trim() } | Select-Object -First 400\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_TVZnpAqEHtL8CWvoHlxy0Dzl|fc_0047bd771936d8e20169cac747a0388195a8b585dedf2e574c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -LiteralPath 'C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shar