?_norm?sz)_align_words_to_timestamps.<locals>._normc?g|]}?|??qSr r r??rr r%r??r?crr r r?rr r%r??r?NZequalr?r4)r?rrr)?splitrZget_opcodes?zip?range)r?r?Zoriginal_wordsZwhisperx_wordsZ\torig_normZwsx_normZmatcherZ\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\lettering_tsx_generator.cpython-310.pyc:2473:word_to_frame?tagZi1Zi2Zj1Zj2r??jr?r rr%?_align_words_to_timestamps~s4\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\lettering_tsx_generator.cpython-310.pyc:2499:?qH|\tS)aYResolve trigger_word -> trigger_frame using word_timestamps from planner batches.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\lettering_tsx_generator.cpython-310.pyc:2503:planner_batches: List of planner batch dicts with scenes containing word_timestamps\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\lettering_tsx_generator.cpython-310.pyc:2520:Optional[int]cCs?|r|sdSt?dd|???}|D]\\}}}t?dd|???}||kr'|Sq|D]\\}}}t?dd|???}|?|?sB|?|?rF|Sq*|D]\\}}}t?dd|???}||vs_||vrc|SqIdS)aFind the frame where trigger_word appears in word_timestamps.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\lettering_tsx_generator.cpython-310.pyc:2522:word_timestamps format: [[\"word\", start_frame, end_frame], ...]\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\parallel_tts.cpython-310.pyc:51:?selfr+r,r-r.r5Zwhisperx_servicer7Ztranscription_validatorr/r0r1Z\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\content_factory_v3\\shared\\processors\\__pycache__\\parallel_tts.cpython-310.pyc:372:r\\?\tclip_name?pathrur?r?r7r6?used_best_effort?word_timestamps?wordscS?(g|]}t|d?r|j|j|jd??qS??word)r?r?r???hasattrr?r?r??rX?wrrrrZ????z=ParallelTTSProcessor._phase3_gpu_validate.<locals>.<listcomp>r??total_durat