{"type":"message","id":"eddd3d49","parentId":"b8648fbc","timestamp":"2026-03-30T21:26:44.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Posso, sim. E aqui faz sentido.\n\nO pacote certo agora é:\n1. **criar a skill `s1_preflight_checker`**\n2. **criar o contrato central do Supervisor do S1**\n3. **actualizar o mirror do S1 de forma resumida para apontar para isso**\n\nSem mexer no resto do S1 ainda.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0047bd771936d8e20169caea9430408195aeb61e8311e0fbda\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":153,"output":84,"cacheRead":172416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":172653,"cost":{"input":0.00038250000000000003,"output":0.00126,"cacheRead":0.043103999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.044746499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774906000328,"responseId":"resp_0047bd771936d8e20169caea92171481958351ebd4c2690759"}}
