{"type":"message","id":"168ac348","parentId":"2c0cca9f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T21:35:18.976Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xSeFmE0mgIsM6qa2hiPa4yEA|fc_0047bd771936d8e20169caec964ba88195bcfdf1ca53b8288a","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\contracts\\s1_supervisor_contract.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 202 The older `s1_*` naming should not be treated as canonical.\n 203 \n 204 ---\n 205 \n+206 ## Second implemented supervisor skill: `s1_paths_resolver`\n+207 \n+208 ### Purpose\n+209 Resolve and centralize the canonical S1 paths for the run.\n+210 \n+211 ### Scope\n+212 Resolves and optionally creates the directory structure for:\n+213 - `b1_pre_production/`\n+214 - `b1_pre_production/inputs/`\n+215 - `b1_pre_production/intermediate/`\n+216 - `inputs/scene_director/`\n+217 - `inputs/tts_polish/`\n+218 - `intermediate/scene_director/`\n+219 - `intermediate/tts_polish/`\n+220 - canonical output file paths\n+221 - canonical `b1_*` checkpoint file paths\n+222 \n+223 ### Out of scope\n+224 `s1_paths_resolver` does **not**:\n+225 - validate semantic readiness\n+226 - call operators\n+227 - inspect screenplay or polish content\n+228 - perform batching\n+229 \n+230 ### Input shape\n+231 ```json\n+232 {\n+233   \"run_root\": \"C:/.../production/004_fr/2026-03-30_004_fr_001\",\n+234   \"create_dirs\": true\n+235 }\n+236 ```\n+237 \n+238 ### Output shape\n+239 ```json\n+240 {\n+241   \"ok\": true,\n+242   \"run_root\": \"C:/.../production/004_fr/2026-03-30_004_fr_001\",\n+243   \"created_dirs\": true,\n+244   \"paths\": {\n+245     \"b1_root\": \".../b1_pre_production\",\n+246     \"inputs_root\": \".../b1_pre_production/inputs\",\n+247     \"intermediate_root\": \".../b1_pre_production/intermediate\",\n+248     \"screenplay_path\": \".../b1_pre_production/screenplay.json\",\n+249     \"tts_polished_path\": \".../b1_pre_production/tts_polished.json\",\n+250     \"scene_bible_path\": \".../scene_bible.json\",\n+251     \"b1_complete_checkpoint\": \".../checkpoints/b1_complete.json\"\n+252   },\n+253   \"errors\": [],\n+254   \"warnings\": []\n+255 }\n+256 ```\n+257 \n 206 ## Current status summary\n 207 At this stage:\n 208 - the S1 Supervisor is defined as an OpenClaw LLM supervisor\n 209 - deterministic helper skills are being formalized\n-210 - `s1_preflight_checker` is the first concrete supervisor skill to be implemented and used as the entry gate for the sector\n+262 - `s1_preflight_checker` is implemented as the entry gate for the sector\n+263 - `s1_paths_resolver` is implemented as the canonical path/structure resolver for the sector","firstChangedLine":206},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774906518855}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4d1e3b6","parentId":"168ac348","timestamp":"2026-03-30T21:35:30.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Feito.\n\n## O que criei agora\n\n### Skill nova\nCriei:\n- `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\runtime\\s1\\supervisor_skills\\s1_paths_resolver.py`\n\n### O que ela faz\nEla resolve e centraliza os paths canónicos do S1 para uma run, incluindo:\n\n- `b1_pre_production/`\n- `b1_pre_production/inputs/`\n- `b1_pre_production/intermediate/`\n- inputs do `scene_director`\n- inputs do `tts_polish`\n- intermediates do `scene_director`\n- intermediates do `tts_polish`\n- paths dos outputs:\n  - `screenplay.json`\n  - `screenplay_validation.json`\n  - `tts_polished.json`\n  - `polish_validation.json`\n  - `scene_bible.json`\n- paths dos checkpoints:\n  - `b1_step1...`\n  - `b1_step2...`\n  - `b1_step3...`\n  - `b1_step4...`\n  - `b1_step5...`\n  - `b1_complete`\n\nE por default ela já:\n- cria as pastas necessárias\n- devolve tudo estruturado num `paths` manifest\n\n---\n\n## Doc central actualizado\nTambém actualizei:\n- `C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\contracts\\s1_supervisor_contract.md`\n\nAgora o contrato já reconhece:\n- `s1_preflight_checker`\n- `s1_paths_resolver`\n\ne documenta o papel da segunda skill.\n\n---\n\n## Como eu vejo o estado agora\nO Supervisor do S1 já começou a ganhar substrate real:\n\n### Skills já implementadas\n- `s1_preflight_checker`\n- `s1_paths_resolver`\n\nIsto já dá ao supervisor:\n- porta de entrada do setor\n- estrutura canónica de paths\n\nQue são exactamente as duas primeiras coisas que precisávamos tirar de cima dele.\n\n---\n\n## Próximo passo recomendado\nAgora o próximo passo natural é:\n\n# `script_batch_planner`\n\nPorque:\n- é a primeira skill que começa a responder ao problema real dos scripts longos\n- prepara o terreno para o `scene_director`\n- e começa a tornar o S1 batchado real\n\nSe quiseres, eu sigo agora exactamente para ela:\n- definição clara\n- implementação\n- update mínimo de docs.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0047bd771936d8e20169caec9a44248195b599ec842eb81af2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":313,"output":512,"cacheRead":179072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":179897,"cost":{"input":0.0007825000000000001,"output":0.00768,"cacheRead":0.044767999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.05323049999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774906519592,"responseId":"resp_0047bd771936d8e20169caec995a288195acbd101d9dff1527"}}
